Oh, my roommate's name is Jake. He’s studying Mechanical Engineering, so our side of the dorm room is usually a mix of my coding textbooks and his gears and prototypes—it’s an interesting blend of chaos! We're lucky to live right on campus, which makes everything super convenient, though the dining hall food gets old sometimes. As for weekends, my absolute favorite thing is grabbing some friends and hitting the hiking trails right behind the campus.
